Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说吉泽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.45,0:00:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候会觉得开心？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.63,0:00:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么突然这么问？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.60,0:00:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.66,0:00:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉泽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.72,0:00:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.07,0:00:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去帮忙准备晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.13,0:02:03.93,NOTE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dubious move\N————\N国际象棋术语「可疑着」、棋谱中用符号？！表示。\N即这一着对局势的影响并不清楚，但一般认为是不必要的走法。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东南风  风力为2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航路没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.53,0:02:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船舵回正
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船舵回正
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚的星星会很明亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生擒希尔维乌斯作战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.45,0:02:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁涅  桌子擦干净了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆也来摆盘子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉泽  你表现得更开心点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.16,0:02:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那艘希尔维乌斯哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.79,0:02:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再更感动点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢呼雀跃「法姆好厉害啊」那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土豆包要烤焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢焦掉的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焦掉的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:02:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了  我还是自己来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.04,0:03:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点反应好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是那艘「死神」希尔维乌斯对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  「死神」希尔维乌斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你借我这身衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常合身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里很紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不要说这种话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉娅也来说句表决心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「要去生擒希尔维乌斯了！」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希尔维乌斯是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.17,0:03:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是「死神」希尔维乌斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来伺候您用餐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢法式蛋饼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:09.21,Mark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(695,647)}Quiche
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希尔维乌斯是一艘非常厉害的谜之战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2年前在利艾尔西边出现后就消失不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.25,0:04:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有亲眼见过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能抓到幽灵船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.15,0:04:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵船？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会来找坏孩子的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  那是一艘实际存在的战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单枪匹马就击溃了阿德斯联邦的舰队之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以联邦也在疯狂地追捕它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危险了吧  真的需要那样的战舰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会成为很厉害的战斗力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复兴图兰是需要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:04:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土豆包要这样一口咬下去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.27,0:05:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有在看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要露出好吃的表情…才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来  这是秘藏的腌肉哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是生日和收获祭都到来了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆  你生日马上就要到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我马上就要16岁了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  又能吃到肉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic\an8\fs40}誕生日だぜハッピー
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是快乐的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic\an8\fs40}生まれて生きて　土に帰る
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诞生至今  终将回归尘土
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:05:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米…米莉娅殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法式蛋饼变得烂烂的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是希尔维乌斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像鱼一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么弄到的  迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么模糊那什么也搞不清啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也不一定  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  船体的构造是有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.07,0:06:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从些许的情报就能够推测出整体的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听上去很难的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  因为和我们所知的战舰不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道推测手法能准确到什么程度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉泽  这个看上去像什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听声装置？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这个呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般来说是桅杆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:06:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图兰的战船也有这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  有戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从对比物和构造来看  应该没那么大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战列舰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.01,0:07:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  或许是强袭登陆舰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭登陆舰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是之前抓到的那艘？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想象一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想象？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上方平整的地方是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是飞行甲板？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,类似于浮游船坞？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话就很难战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么是战列舰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.75,0:07:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我觉得不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰底有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.39,0:07:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突出的外壳里…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这外壳打开后就会出现很厉害的秘密武器！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:07:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密武器  有的话就有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压舱物？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮呢？  难道是非武装的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密兵器呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才法姆说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是收纳式的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是神出鬼没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有一个国家拥有伪装战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.44,0:08:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将构造复杂化进而隐藏武装的目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据目击情报上说一直只有一艘战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  是负责搜集情报的单独行动舰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不露声色  尽量避免战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有比任何战舰都能率先发现敌人的索敌能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比任何战舰都要迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最麻烦的是在扎进一番叉前我们无法摸清对方的攻击力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能画出这种船
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉赛尔你真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是我的最高杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是「死神」希尔维乌斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有许多谜之秘密武器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.98,0:09:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒上水后就大功告成啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗里兹  别睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但确实是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一个不可思议的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  他大概是在半年前突然出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后不知不觉就混熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.63,0:09:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技术确实不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但性格却让人难以捉摸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉娅  你肚子饿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳公公的味道最足的还属泰蕾莎阿姨晒的被子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉娅  你要喝水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.07,0:10:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那么在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好客气的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就当是在自己家里…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然小了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久没叫人来住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.26,0:10:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉赛尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久前来过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉泽必须要照顾鲁涅他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.31,0:10:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你睡床上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.01,0:11:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉娅是客人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉娅睡床上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡地上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下能睡着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会说出那么令人意外的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至把卡尔特法尔的各位都卷进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不是希尔维乌斯也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.31,0:11:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想既然要干就瞄准大的猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样会更加开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让米莉娅开心起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是服了你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  米莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安  法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安  米莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一番叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰艇？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.18,0:12:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我听见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  我们去猎死神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会复兴图兰的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请保佑我吧  父王  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.59,0:13:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行啊  公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.97,0:13:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我好好享…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  你这身礼服真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  昨晚你明明还信心十足
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  我相信吉泽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定能行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:13:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和法姆的先锋艇感觉不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱碰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那里是魯修拉的座位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.22,NOTE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁修拉\N————\N前作「LAST EXILE」登场角色、迪奥的亲信。将迪奥视为自己的一切。\N年幼时被戴芬妮作为玩具送给迪奥、但迪奥却将他当作朋友。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好把嘴闭上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回旋！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  快停下…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直是人间美味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆  睡得香吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香到都掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是第8次了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.91,0:14:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲸鱼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚睡醒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在这附近…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低速航行中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  就按平时的那套作战方案来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方可是死神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为是谜之战舰  所以才不需要耍什么花招
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.11,0:14:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉娅  连泰蒂也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算叫我回去  我也不会听的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为回不去了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罢  你就看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了米莉娅我一定会生擒希尔维乌斯的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方距离3万  舰影数7
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认到了信号弹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,识别代码  联邦舰克温格
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舵10度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舵10度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲸鱼改变了航向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只笨鸵鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  抢下了一番叉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛西莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像说了「一番叉」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航速低下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:15:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的「狩猎鲸鱼」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像乐在其中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.55,0:16:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  成功地拖住了它的脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还轰隆隆地前进吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神由我来打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.05,0:16:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是那招吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航向前方  距离500
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现大量岩礁  右舵20度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上升至75
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的耳朵真灵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.24,0:16:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就堵上它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.81,0:16:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽丝  之后就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视觉听觉全被摧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵舰已毫无胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我卡尔特法尔的法姆·芳·方会将你们引导到安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉娅会感到高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是小孩子在玩战争游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.57,0:17:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希尔维乌斯正在逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  再来摧毁一次听声装置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甩不掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉强算是及格吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀飞行就差远了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:48.40,Mark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(557,647)}scissors
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:48.40,NOTE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀飞行(scissors)\N————\N飞行技巧、因平行飞行的两机进行交叉飞行的轨道如同剪刀一般而得名。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去帮她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.01,0:17:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要帮？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  她是那么地乐在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她打算撞过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人没有反击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然赤手空拳上战场  真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也让我加入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.96,0:18:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.46,0:18:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉泽  鲸鱼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了  4点钟方向  距离4000
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神圣之湖？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣域被…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罢手吧  就此放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是为你而制定的作战计划哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  我绝不会让神圣之湖受到玷污的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.63,0:19:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉泽  快发射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一发  吉泽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  让克劳迪亚装置停止运转我果然做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在训练中没有一次成功过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.76,0:19:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从外面不行的话  里面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  吉泽一定能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直行6秒后上升
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.38,0:19:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.89,0:19:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种类型的舰艇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.72,0:20:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,底部说不定是空荡荡的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.46,0:20:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡航  右转
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.71,0:20:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉泽真厉害  名不虚传
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒上水后就大功告成啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水密门！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:14.21,NOTE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水密门\N————\N船内水密舱壁和围壁上所装的不透水金属门。\N从这空中战舰一般不会配备的装置中可以看出希尔维乌斯的特殊性。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  快出去  法姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外部水密门关闭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.14,0:20:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中部甲板乘员转移完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体乘员固定好自己的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快退回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样  为什么舰艇会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:20:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉泽  我梦见鲸鱼潜水了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.00,0:21:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海洋与天空都能自由驰骋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然已经看到了希尔维乌斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.49,0:21:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不能放你们活着回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是刚才的那个红色家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这艘战舰的舰长塔琪安娜·维斯拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是卡尔特法尔的法姆·芳·方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.77,0:21:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你多大了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是吉赛尔·柯雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.39,0:21:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两人都是15岁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.11,0:21:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果愿意协助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定可以把你们放回空中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.81,0:21:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要我们做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.06,0:21:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你几岁就夺几艘阿德斯联邦的战舰过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几岁夺几艘…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.63,0:21:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15艘是不可能的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.62,0:21:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对小孩子来说负担太重了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.01,0:22:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就抢给你看看  15艘！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.13,0:22:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆  吉赛尔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.08,0:22:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉娅…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.99,0:22:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接受你的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.91,0:22:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要为米莉娅组建起一支舰队
